Mitchells & Butlers to Appoint Ivell as Chairman, Times Says

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 
2011-10-23T11:40:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/mitchells-butlers-to-appoint-ivell-as-chairman-times-says.html
Mitchells & Butlers Plc (MAB)  is close to
naming Bob Ivell as chairman on a permanent basis, the Sunday
Times reported, without saying where it got the information.  Ivell has been interim chairman since July, according to
the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
